Package edu.neu.ccis.sms.entity.submissions

Hibernate Entity classes for Document (submission document for a member), Evaluation (evaluation for a document), enum EvalType (signifies different types of final evaluation calculation strategies)

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Document
    Hibernate Entity bean class for Document; Encompasses a submission done by user, resubmissions for a given member just update the old Document instance
    Evaluation
    Hibernate Entity bean class for Evaluation; contains evaluation results for a Document by a single reviewer

    Enum Description
    EvalType
    Decides what are final evaluation strategy types to calculate the final grades for a submitted-document - e.g.
